<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3708168>
    dc:description "Figure 8. Orotaygetis surui n. sp., genitalia. a) Male genitalia in lateral view. b) Phallus in lateral view. c) Female genitalia with posterior portion enlarged. d) Lamella antevaginalis in ventral view. e) Corpus bursae with focus on signa (illustrated genitalia: MUSM-LEP 102416 for male; SN-16-60 for female)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3708168/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

